# Trivy ignore file — list of vuln / misconfig / secret rule IDs to suppress.
# One ID per line. Comments start with `#`.
#
# Add an entry only after triaging the finding via upstream docs / source.
# Mirror the rationale in security/SECURITY.md (Trivy exceptions table).
#
# Examples:
#   CVE-2023-12345   # accepted: only triggers in non-default config
#   AVD-KSV-0014     # accepted: see SECURITY.md row
